{"tid":2147287,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學佛][阿彌陀佛] 誠是自己的真性，誠是自己的性德。","createTime":"2020-08-09T06:49:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T16:56:33.000Z","uid":347001,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"964897a9f253b851393d3e1e29f40acebad95bcd","tid":2147287,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nbb8xxh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnbb8xxh.jpg&h=877c4605&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n淨空法師：誠一定要學，為什麼？<strong><span class=\"pink\"><span class=\"x-large\">誠是自己的真性，誠是自己的性德。</span></span></strong><strong><span class=\"gold\">別人騙我，不要緊，他的事情，我不騙人，這要懂得，絕不騙人。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"large\">如果對我傷害，不開口就好了。別人來問問題，明知道回答他，對自己很不利，回答阿彌陀佛，這就好。不管問什麼問題，都是阿彌陀佛，阿彌陀佛解決一切問題。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"pink\">真的對他有好處，一歷耳根，永為道種，這是我們對他最殊勝、最圓滿的善意。念念、聲聲，把阿彌陀佛介紹給他，接受也好，不接受也得接受，總是聽進去了。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以言語是神咒，我們總結，真誠的言語就是神咒，能夠跟十善業相應。真誠的言語，不妄語，不兩舌，不綺語，不惡口，這個言語就是神咒，就能跟天地鬼神感應道交，就叫消融咒，消化、融化之咒，消融。<br />\n<br />\n🎬淨空法師開示影片：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zYs-lrMgFbA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzYs-lrMgFbA&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminCTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=d74c3222\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zYs-lrMgFbA</a><br />\n<br />\n🙏更多淨空法師開示請點選上方主頁<br />\n<br />\n🌷華藏衛視LINE：<a href=\"http://nav.cx/fWLlL9y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnav.cx%2FfWLlL9y&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminCTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=ceabdcf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://nav.cx/fWLlL9y</a>"},{"pid":"7a759930f5c6004a323e70c8b43780c3ee9f50c0","tid":2147287,"uid":347001,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"964897a9f253b851393d3e1e29f40acebad95bcd","tid":2147287,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:49: